    "description": "BSE Global Group is actively seeking a talented and motivated Investment Banker to join our dynamic team in Jabalpur. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout BSE Global Group:\nBSE Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BSE Global Group!",
